======================================================================
VQE ANSATZ: USING FOURIER STRUCTURE FOR QUANTUM OPTIMIZATION
======================================================================
  H ≈ H_0 + H_2 (97% of energy)
  H_2 depends only on score sequence (1 DOF)
  Score = sum_j Z_j for each vertex

  PROPOSED VQE CIRCUIT:
  1. Initialize |+⟩^m (uniform superposition)
  2. Apply R_z(θ) rotations on each qubit (parametric)
  3. Apply ZZ coupling gates for adjacent edge pairs
  4. Measure Z expectation values
  5. Estimate H_2 from score sequence
  6. Add degree-4 correction from ZZ-ZZ correlators

  Circuit depth: O(m) for H_2, O(m^2) for H_4 correction
  For n=5: 10 qubits, depth ~10 for 97% accuracy
  For n=7: 21 qubits, depth ~21 for estimated 97% accuracy
  For n=19: 171 qubits, depth ~171 — feasible on near-term quantum hardware!

